column18: Automatic Alerting - the system automatically sends an emergency 911 alert and informs your family if you've taken a fall and haven't moved for more than a few minutes
column19: On-demand alerting - you initiate an emergency alert with the system when you need help
column21: Works both indoors and outdoors - the system monitors you in all environments
column22: Interactive with buttons and lights - the system has a simple interface with just buttons and status lights
column23: Interactive with a touchscreen display - the system has a full-fledged touchscreen interface
column24: Always-on: the system is always-on and does not require recharging etc.
column25: Injury reduction: the system also reduces the injury from the fall by using foam, inflatable airbags etc
